 life to rescue his brother Benjamin.

231
00:25:18,160 --> 00:25:22,160
 And the tribe of Judah was the largest.

232
00:25:22,160 --> 00:25:29,520
 And he, the tribe of Judah, was the leader of the other 11 tribes.

233
00:25:29,520 --> 00:25:37,240
 And he was also privileged, being part of the lineage of the Messiah.

