 of Revelation.

236
00:25:47,640 --> 00:26:04,120
 Church, we live in the days when the behavior of Judah and Tamar are very, very common.

237
00:26:04,120 --> 00:26:10,760
 But there's no restriction of God doing what he intends to do.

